What you need to know:

Kamworor’s replacement is one of the sweeping changes Athletics Kenya have made to the team they had initially picked for the eventAK director of competitions, Paul Mutwii disclosed that they have entered a team of 10 athletes; five men and five women for the 24th edition of the world half marathonBesides Jepchirchir, who hold women’s only half marathon world record of 1:05:34, the team has former mixed women’s half marathon world record holder Joyciline Jepkosgei (1:04:51)